<title>bdạyẗ jdydẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (hl lkẖạṭy zyy ḍʿyf .. ạ̹nh yyjy lmḥḍrk
 mạḍy ṣʿb wmkẖyf .. wạlsẖr zạd wạmtlk)2
 (ạ̉nạ ʿạyz ậjy lk nạdyny .. ạftḥ ly bạb ạlrjạ
 ạ̉nạ jrḥy nạfdẖ wʿyny .. mkswrẗ wmḥrjẗ)2
 2- (ạ̉nạ ʿạrf ạ̹nh fy dmk .. ksr qywdy ạlḥdyd
 ạqblny ʿbdk wạbnk .. ạkẖlqny mn jdyd)2
 (ạ̉nạ ʿạyz ậjy lk wkẖạyf .. ạ̉ḍʿf tạny wạ̉rjʿ
 ḍmny qwl ly hạsạndk .. wfy wqt ạlḍʿf hạrfʿ)2
 wfy wqt ạlḍʿf hạrfʿ
 3- (ạ̉nạ jạy wạ̉mly tkwn ly .. ạ̉bwyạ wsndy ạlsẖdyd
 mạlysẖ bdyl tạny swạk .. ạ̹nt ạ̉mly ạlwḥyd)2
 (kẖlyny ạ̉bll ktạfk .. bdmwʿ twbty wṣlạty
 wạ̉bdạ̉ ạlywm mʿạk .. bdạyẗ jdydẗ lḥyạty)2</lyrics>
